'''Asana''' ({{IPAc-en|ə|ˈ|s|ɑː|n|ə}},而不是 '''''Asana''''')<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kiLCmstyDdM |title=Asana: The modern way to work together |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archive-date=2014-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103124637/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kiLCmstyDdM |dead-url=no }}</ref> 是一个网络和[[流動軟件應用程式|移动应用]]，它的设计是为了改善团队交流和协作的方式。2008年[[达斯廷·莫斯科维茨|达斯廷·莫斯科维茨]]离开Facebook，与贾斯丁·罗森斯坦一起创办了阿萨纳。<ref name="Who is the CEO of Asana?">Rosenstein, Justin.[http://www.quora.com/Who-is-the-CEO-of-Asana "Reply on Quora to: Who is the CEO of Asana?"], [[Quora|Quora]], February 8, 2011. Retrieved 2011-02-15.</ref> 在[[Facebook|Facebook]]时，他们一起工作以改善其员工的工作效率。<ref>{{cite news|last=Guynn|first=Jessica|title=Facebook co-founder Dustin Moskovitz unveils new company, Asana|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2011/11/facebook-co-founder-dustin-moskovitz-unveils-new-company-.html|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2 November 2011|accessdate=2013-12-28|archive-date=2014-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140119075438/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2011/11/facebook-co-founder-dustin-moskovitz-unveils-new-company-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>Asana如今被数以千计的团队所使用<ref>{{cite web|last=Kaplan|first=Dan|title=Announcing Inbox: A Step Towards A Post-Email World|url=http://blog.asana.com/2012/06/asana-launches-inbox/|accessdate=27 June 2012|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103204724/http://blog.asana.com/2012/06/asana-launches-inbox/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中包括公司如[[Twitter|Twitter]]、[[Foursquare|Foursquare]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Hamburger|first=Ellis|title=With big Asana update, Facebook co-founder Moskovitz wants to kill email|url=http://www.theverge.com/2012/6/27/3120466/asana-inbox|newspaper=The Verge|date=27 June 2012|accessdate=2013-12-28|archive-date=2014-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108040521/http://www.theverge.com/2012/6/27/3120466/asana-inbox|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[LinkedIn|LinkedIn]]、[[Disqus|Disqus]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://asana.com/customers |title=Asana Customers |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |accessdate=January 19, 2013 |archive-date=2014-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122052841/https://asana.com/customers |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[Airbnb|Airbnb]]、Rdio、AdParlor、Flapps、GDG Shanghai、TECH2IPO<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tech2ipo.com/64231 |title=创见聚光灯之团队协作工具：我们的选择> |accessdate=April 2, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407070825/http://tech2ipo.com/64231 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[優步|優步]]和Entelo<ref>{{cite news|last=Constine|first=Josh|title=Twitter and LinkedIn Manage Tasks With Asana, New API Means Robots Can Too|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/04/21/asana-stats/|newspaper=TechCrunch|date=21 April 2012|accessdate=2013-12-28|archive-date=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224050212/http://techcrunch.com/2012/04/21/asana-stats/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==API==
2012年4月，Asana把它们的[[API|API]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Slovacek|first=Greg|title=Announcing the Asana API|url=http://blog.asana.com/2012/04/announcing-the-asana-api/|accessdate=19 April 2012|archive-date=2013-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130628002313/http://blog.asana.com/2012/04/announcing-the-asana-api/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 开放给了第三方开发者。有Asana账户的任何人都可以免费使用其应用程序接口（API），通过他们的开发者网站来使用其应用程序接口。<ref>{{cite web|title=The Asana API|url=http://developer.asana.com/|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213024126/http://developer.asana.com/|archivedate=2013-12-13|accessdate=2013-12-28}}</ref>

